 The <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.Modifiers%2A> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard> class is the set of the modifier keys that are currently pressed.  
  
 Some [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_api#plural](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-apisharpplural-md.md)] in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)] that make use of the ModifierKeys enumeration are the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.Modifiers%2A> properties on the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyGesture>, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseGesture> classes.  
  
